Title : Chinese Curling Association
Text : {{short description|Sports governing body}}
'''Chinese Curling Association''' is the governing body for the sport of [[curling]] in [[China|the People's Republic of China]]. It has been a member of the [[World Curling Federation]] since 2002.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldcurling.org/wcf-member-associations|title=WCF Member Associations|publisher=World Curling Federation|accessdate=25 April 2014}}</ref>

